Name: Average duration of 'Accepted + In Progress' before transitioning to 'Completed + In Call'
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Accepted + In Progress' and activity 'Completed + In Call'

Name: Average duration from 'Accepted + In Progress' to 'Completed + Closed' across all cases
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Accepted + In Progress' and activity 'Completed + Closed'

Name: Total duration of 'Accepted + In Progress' activity across all cases

Name: Longest duration of 'Accepted + In Progress' before any transition
Metric: the maximum of the duration between the first time instant when `ACTIVITY` == 'Accepted + In Progress' and the last time instant when <ppinot4py.model.states.RuntimeState object at 0x000001E27CECF0A0> - AppliesTo.PROCESS

Name: Shortest duration of 'Accepted + In Progress' before transitioning to any activity
Metric: The minimum of the duration between activity Accepted + In Progress and the end of the case

Name: Total duration of 'Accepted + In Progress' before 'Completed + In Call' across cases with 'Completed + In Call' as a final activity

Name: Average duration between 'Accepted + In Progress' and 'Accepted + Assigned' across all variants

Name: Longest single instance of 'Accepted + In Progress' across all cases
Metric: the maximum of the duration between the first time instant when `ACTIVITY` == 'Accepted + In Progress' and the last time instant when <ppinot4py.model.states.RuntimeState object at 0x000001E27CECF0A0> - AppliesTo.PROCESS

Name: Shortest duration from 'Accepted + In Progress' to 'Completed + In Call' in any case
Metric: The minimum of the duration between activity 'Accepted + In Progress' and activity 'Completed + In Call'

Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Accepted + In Progress' and activity 'Accepted + Wait - Implementation'
